    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span style=\"color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">Forces the target, if damaged by the arrow&rsquo;s attack, to make a DC 20 Fortitude save or be slain immediately. It takes one day to make an arrow of death, and the arrow only functions for the arcane archer who created it. The arrow of death lasts no longer than one year, and the archer can only have one such arrow in existence at a time.</span></p>",
      "chat": "",
      "unidentified": "<p>A standard (common) arrow used as a melee weapon is treated as a light improvised weapon (&ndash;4 penalty on attack rolls) and deals damage as a dagger of its size (critical multiplier &times;2). Unless indicated otherwise, arrows come in a leather quiver that holds 20 arrows.</p>"
